(84, 1, '2020-05-08 18:28:27', '2020-05-08 11:28:27', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":42,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/wordpress_1-1024x405.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-42\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Gi·ªõi thi·ªáu</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">WordPress l√† m·ªôt ph·∫ßn m·ªÅm ngu·ªìn m·ªü (Open Source Software) ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·∫øt b·∫±ng ng√¥n ng·ªØ l·∫≠p tr√¨nh PHP v√† s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h·ªá qu·∫£n tr·ªã c∆° s·ªü d·ªØ li·ªáu MySQL. WordPress ƒë∆∞·ª£c ra m·∫Øt l·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n v√†o ng√†y 27/5/2003 b·ªüi t√°c gi·∫£ Matt Mullenweg v√† Mike Little. Hi·ªán nay WordPress ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ªü h·ªØu v√† ph√°t tri·ªÉn b·ªüi c√¥ng ty Automattic c√≥ tr·ª• s·ªü t·∫°i San Francisco, California, M·ªπ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">WordPress l√† m·ªôt m√£ ngu·ªìn m·ªü b·∫±ng ng√¥n ng·ªØ PHP ƒë·ªÉ h·ªó tr·ª£ t·∫°o blog c√° nh√¢n, v√† n√≥ ƒë∆∞·ª£c r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu ng∆∞·ªùi s·ª≠ d·ª•ng ·ªßng h·ªô v·ªÅ t√≠nh d·ªÖ s·ª≠ d·ª•ng, nhi·ªÅu t√≠nh nƒÉng h·ªØu √≠ch. Qua th·ªùi gian, s·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng ng∆∞·ªùi s·ª≠ d·ª•ng tƒÉng l√™n, c√°c c·ªông t√°c vi√™n l√† nh·ªØng l·∫≠p tr√¨nh vi√™n c≈©ng tham gia ƒë√¥ng ƒë·∫£o ƒë·ªÉ ph√°t tri·ªÉn m√£ ngu·ªìn WordPress c√≥ th√™m nh·ªØng t√≠nh nƒÉng tuy·ªát v·ªùi. V√† cho ƒë·∫øn 2015, WordPress ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c xem nh∆∞ l√† m·ªôt h·ªá qu·∫£n tr·ªã n·ªôi dung (CMS ‚Äì Content Management System) v∆∞·ª£t tr·ªôi ƒë·ªÉ h·ªó tr·ª£ ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng t·∫°o ra nhi·ªÅu th·ªÉ lo·∫°i website kh√°c nhau nh∆∞ blog, website tin t·ª©c/t·∫°p ch√≠, gi·ªõi thi·ªáu doanh nghi·ªáp, b√°n h√†ng ‚Äì th∆∞∆°ng m·∫°i ƒëi·ªán t·ª≠, th·∫≠m ch√≠ v·ªõi c√°c lo·∫°i website c√≥ ƒë·ªô ph·ª©c t·∫°p cao nh∆∞ ƒë·∫∑t ph√≤ng kh√°ch s·∫°n, thu√™ xe, ƒëƒÉng d·ª± √°n b·∫•t ƒë·ªông s·∫£n,‚Ä¶ H·∫ßu nh∆∞ m·ªçi h√¨nh th·ª©