c <strong>Lu·ªìng</strong> hi·ªÉn th·ªã t·∫•t c·∫£ th√¥ng tin m√† m·ªçi th√†nh vi√™n trong l·ªõp chia s·∫ª l√™n Classroom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ chia s·∫ª b·∫±ng c√°ch ch·ªçn v√†o khung ‚Äúchia s·∫ª ƒë√¥i ƒëi·ªÅu v·ªÅ l·ªõp h·ªçc‚ÄùB·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ chia s·∫ª th√¥ng tin v√† ƒëƒÉng t·∫£i th√™m t·ªáp. Ho√†n th√†nh b·∫±ng n√∫t <strong>ƒêƒÉng</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":163,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Xem b√†i t·∫≠p v√† n·ªôp b√†i cho gi√°o vi√™n</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ xem t·∫•t c·∫£ b√†i t·∫≠p ƒë√£ upload l√™n Classroom ·ªü m·ª•c <strong>B√†i t·∫≠p tr√™n l·ªõp</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":164,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_9-1024x818.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-164\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ƒê·ªÉ xem b√†i t·∫≠p c√° nh√¢n c·ªßa m√¨nh th√¨ ch·ªçn <strong>Xem b√†i t·∫≠p c·ªßa b·∫°n</strong>. M·ªôt giao di·ªán m·ªõi hi·ªÉn th·ªã to√†n b·ªô nh·ªØng b√†i t·∫≠p d√†nh cho b·∫°n v√† t√¨nh tr·∫°ng ƒë√£ n·ªôp hay ch∆∞a</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":165,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_10.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-165\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ƒê·ªÉ hi·ªÉn th·ªã chi ti·∫øt ch√∫ng ta nh·∫•n v√†o t·ª´ng b√†i t·∫≠p ƒë·ªÉ xem chi ti·∫øt.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":166,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_11-1024x768.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-166\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Th√™m file ƒë√≠nh k√®m: Sinh vi√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ g·ª≠i n·ªôi dung b√†i ƒëƒÉng d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng m·ªôt t·∫≠p tin ƒë√≠nh k√®m t·ª´ m√°y sinh vi√™n, ho·∫∑c t·ª´ Drive trong h·ªôp th∆∞ c·ªßa sinh vi√™n. Ngo√†i ra sinh vi√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ g·ª≠i m·ªôt n·ªôi dung d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng video ƒë∆∞·ª£c thu h√¨nh s·∫µn (ƒë∆∞·ª£c upload l√™n Youtube) , ho·∫∑c m·ªôt ƒë·ªãa ch·ªâ website li√™n quan ƒë·∫øn b√†i ƒëƒÉng c·ªßa m√¨nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi t·∫°o xong sinh vi√™n nh·∫•n <strong>ƒêƒÇNG</strong> ƒë·ªÉ g·ª≠i n·ªôi dung cho c√°c b·∫°n trong l·ªõp.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ho·∫∑c sinh vi√™n c≈©ng c√≥ th·ªÉ th√™m c√°c nh·∫≠n x√©t v·ªÅ b√†i t·∫≠p: nh·∫≠n x√©t c√≥ th·ªÉ l√† c√¥ng khai n·∫øu mu·ªën m·ªçi ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë·ªÅu ƒë·ªçc ƒë∆∞·ª£c ho·∫∑c l√† nh·∫≠n x√©t ri√™ng t∆∞ ƒë·ªÉ gi√°o vi√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë·ªçc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>H·ªßy ƒëƒÉng k√Ω l·ªõp h·ªçc</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V√¨ m·ªôt l√Ω do n√†o ƒë√≥, c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒëƒÉng k√Ω nh·∫ßm,‚Ä¶ sinh vi√™n c·∫ßn h·ªßy l·ªõp h·ªçc ƒë√£ ƒëƒÉng k√Ω. ƒë·ªÉ h·ªßy l·ªõp h·ªçc, b·∫°n c·∫ßn nh·∫•n v√†o bi·ªÉu t∆∞·ª£ng <img width=\"33\" height=\"36\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/LddHj2PAqlZ4oAMXR6LD_24eIs3ZbUqNmf333WCJlipdKV3R3NzoEb2ceUJB3foh6RhJqc8TQJoluyo-XWiPbhdBnA60E3-4WPDhcYggNaCXZEHTrq-2awFlFtI3DLCApkGV3LxzzlH_JZt36A\"> ·ªü tr√°i tr√™n c√πng c·ªßa trang web v√† ch·ªçn v√†o <strong>L·ªõp h·ªçc</strong> ƒë·ªÉ tr·ªü v·ªÅ danh s√°ch c√°c l·ªõp h·ªçc ƒë√£ tham gia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":167,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_12.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-167\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>T√¨m ƒë·∫øn l·ªõp h·ªçc mu·ªën h·ªßy ch·ªçn v√†o bi·ªÉu t∆∞·ª£ng <img width=\"32\" height=\"46\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/34PWywFYhPXNpEL1pmwMBK_NSUE5Xv5BNQZCjLvTjROywWDyk3_rZY1zNiiC0Sofvk4-R_IGXBqreFFkBMyKE3BwKW4O0dYnyOXx4UaxF0_pXpCMojNpy1wldUeqgRn5WmqoE4WkXIBafft1-A\"> v√† ch·ªçn <strong>H·ªßy ƒëƒÉng k√Ω</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":168,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_13.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-168\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>M·ªôt th√¥ng b√°o s·∫Ω hi·ªán l√™n. B·∫°n nh·∫•n <strong>H·ªßy ƒëƒÉng k√Ω</strong> ƒë·ªÉ x√°c nh·∫≠n r·ªùi kh·ªèi l·ªõp h·ªçc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ggclassroom_14.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V·∫≠y l√† b·∫°n ƒë√£ bi·∫øt nh·ªØng ch·ª©c nƒÉng c≈©ng nh∆∞ c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c∆° b·∫£n nh·∫•t v·ªõi Google Classroom r·ªìi ƒë·∫•y!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"right\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right\"><strong>Thanh B√πi</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'H∆∞·ªõng D·∫´n S·ª≠ D·ª•ng Google Classroom Cho Sinh Vi√™n', 'H∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c√°c ch·ª©c nƒÉng c√≥ trong Google Classroom', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '99-au